@startuml
title Skill Discovery & Execution Sequence

participant "Run Orchestrator" as ORC
participant "FileSystem" as FS
participant "Engine Adapter" as ADAPT
participant "CLI Tool" as CLI

ORC -> FS: List contents of /skills and /agents
FS --> ORC: Return directory list
ORC -> ORC: Match agent name with available skills

ORC -> ADAPT: execute_run(prompt, skills)
ADAPT -> FS: Read SKILL.md for context
FS --> ADAPT: SKILL.md content

ADAPT -> ADAPT: Inject SKILL.md into Prompt
ADAPT -> CLI: exec --include-directories /skills/xyz --prompt "..."
CLI -> CLI: Process with local context
CLI --> ADAPT: CLI Output
ADAPT --> ORC: Final Result
@enduml
